<br><br>According to the Labour Force Survey, <strong>441,000</strong> working people sustained an injury at work in 2020/21 (Health and Safety Executive, 2022). Would you know what to do? Not all work environments have a first aid kit at hand or the correct contents. 
<br><br>In this blog, <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/dr-richard-dune-blog" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">Dr Richard Dune</span></em></a> will identify common misconceptions about emergency first aid in the workplace.
