</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-54_">Volunteer staff.
 
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-56_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-57_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-58_">What is covered in emergency first aid at work courses?
